---
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Delilah’s Journey</title>

    <style>
      @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@600;700;800&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap');

      body {
        margin: 0;
        background: #f8f5f2;
        color: #1f1a17;
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      main {
        max-width: 820px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 60px 24px;
      }

      nav {
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      nav a {
        margin-right: 1rem;
        color: #7a2e2e;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      h1, h2 {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        color: #2c1d18;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 3.2rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      .hero-tag {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        padding: 0.35rem 0.8rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: #ead9cf;
        color: #5d2a2a;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      section {
        background: #fffdfb;
        border: 1px solid #eadfd7;
        border-radius: 18px;
        padding: 28px;
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }

      a {
        color: #7a2e2e;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <main>
      <nav>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/about/">About</a>
        <a href="/blog/">Blog</a>
      </nav>

      <span class="hero-tag">Life Insurance Journey</span>

      <h1>Delilah’s Journey</h1>

      <p>
        Documenting my journey as a life insurance agent — the failures, growth,
        and lessons behind becoming licensed and building something meaningful.
      </p>

      <section>
        <h2>Why I Started</h2>
        <p>
          I didn’t start this journey with confidence — I started it with uncertainty.
          Failing my exams more than once made me question myself, but I kept going.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Featured Post</h2>
        <p>Start here with the beginning of my journey.</p>
        <a href="/posts/post-1/">From Initial Hire to Licensed Agent</a>
      </section>
    </main>

    <!-- THIS IS WHAT MAKES YOUR SOCIALS SHOW -->
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>